<span class="literal">-</span> <span class="comment">fixed</span>
</code></pre><p>기본은 static이다. 아무것도 설정하지 않았다면 static 이다. </p>]]></description><link>http://withfpp.github.com/post/css-haegsim1-css-essential-1)</link><guid isPermaLink="false">css-haegsim1-css-essential-1)</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[<a href="" target="_blank">Leon Taeho Kim</a>]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 28 Aug 2014 11:20:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title><![CDATA[Welcome to haroopress]]></title><description><![CDATA[<img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/a8618a255192bd842fdd62d099776735?r=pg&s=48.jpg&d=identicon"><br/><h3 id="toc_20">환영합니다.</h3>

